data.description: This 2 bed 1 bath charmer is move-in ready and a potential investment opportunity! With original hardwood floors in the living room and bedrooms, this gem is sure to feel like home. This home offers convenience like no other as it is close to parks, shopping, and restaurants. Be sure to check out the newly renovated bathroom that has new tile throughout the tub, and the spacious kitchen that boasts numerous cabinets. Don't forget the unfinished, waterproofed basement with ample storage opportunities.   Updates per the seller: Tankless Water Heater(2019), HVAC(2019), Windows (2019), Tile Work (2021), Basement Waterproofing (2021). Seller is offering a $499 2-10 home warranty for peace of mind.
